 1997-04151997-03-190,  ,  CAN PORTS,  TC,  , 
PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 1984-4/168 which authorize the VANCOUVER PORT CORPORATION (a) to accept the surrender of a lease held by Canadian International College Inc. with respect to some 2.619 hectares of land in North Vancouver, (b) to sell the demised premises to the College, and (c) to revise the Agreement to sell the remainder of the property (Maplewood North) to UNITED PROPERTIES LIMITED.
